demo_checklist.md
mitre_coverage_report.md
docs
evaluation/results
experiment

# --- Tests / sample artifacts ---
tests/__pycache__
samples/pcap/*
!samples/pcap/.gitkeep

# --- Local volumes / runtime ---
logs
*.pid
*.sock

# --- CI / claude / harness ---
.claude
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
